data.description: Welcome this beautiful home to the market! Nestled in the center of one Paragould's most sought after subdivisions, 2702 Stonegate Drive is a three bedroom, two bath house with plenty of space and charm. A two car garage and a heated and cooled shop offer even more space to check all the boxes on your future home's list. This property offers a fully fenced yard a spacious manicured front lawn. Come check out this lovely home!
